<refsect1>
<title>Description</title>
<para>This directive is deprecated, please use &gt;Limit SITE_CHMOD&lt;
instead.</para>

<para>
AllowChmod allows control over whether the &quot;SITE CHMOD&quot;
command is allowed to clients.</para>
</refsect1>

